In addition, those who do not make many kilometers per year will be able to opt for the i-Stop version associated only with the 150-horsepower 2.0 petrol engine.
The only drawback of this model is its high price, which is between EUR 21,770 for the Luxury finish and EUR 23 270 for the model tested, the Sportive.
In return for this large sum, the Mazda3 will offer us a great dose of satisfaction every day.
